{"tid":2432010,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"施德來妻 憑書感念丈夫","createTime":"2021-03-04T04:33:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-04T04:33:09.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0d2ddb6f5dc7be43d55a347fef80f06e4f175e6e","tid":2432010,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T04:33:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210304/QZBCFZR5FJHO5KYJZRK5ZURUB4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210304%2FQZBCFZR5FJHO5KYJZRK5ZURUB4%2F&d=Xhragic3nybqeCAZBODyv3psBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=c747f574\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210304%2FQZBCFZR5FJHO5KYJZRK5ZURUB4%2F&h=f33a728e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210304/QZBCFZR5FJHO5KYJZRK5ZURUB4/</a><br />\n<br />\n施德來妻 憑書感念丈夫<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Mxo2-I4R1aZTQqsSsizOBw7H1UY=/1000x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SPEH2Y4ZFFDLNH7IAWBYRAWJVI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FMxo2-I4R1aZTQqsSsizOBw7H1UY%3D%2F1000x563%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSPEH2Y4ZFFDLNH7IAWBYRAWJVI.jpg&h=aa79683d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】47名被告保釋申請的馬拉松式聆訊，對眾被告的親屬同樣是一場煎熬，其中數名被告的妻子三天以來只能在庭外透過視像直播看到丈夫，心裏除了擔心他們的身體狀況，還要為保釋申請結果作最壞的打算。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：鄒家成：不分光譜渡難關<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n余思朗：已為保釋結果預備<br />\n<br />\n被告岑敖暉的新婚太太余思朗批評聆訊太過漫長，對家屬、律師及記者而言，都不是好事，目前主要擔心各被告的精神及健康狀況，「四日冇換過衫，聽日又唔知搞到幾點，如果冇得保釋又唔知幾時送到物資」。對於保釋結果，余稱已有兩手準備及作好心理預備。<br />\n<br />\n余又表示，知道岑敖暉等人昨早有看報紙，<span class=\"orange\">並引述岑指知悉這幾天法庭外的狀況，對有很多市民前來支持他們，感到十分鼓舞及感動。</span><br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：李予信媽媽 戴愛兒黑帽聽審<br />\n<br />\n黃大仙區議員施德來的太太（圖）昨天隻身一人到庭，並帶同丈夫推薦的政治書，指希望藉書本感受丈夫閱讀此書的感覺，在開審後她便目不轉睛地緊盯着螢幕「小電視」，希望能找到不見多日的丈夫身影，其間她的精神顯得略為緊張，更不時緊握雙手。<br />\n<br />\n昨日輪到前立法會議員朱凱廸為保釋申請陳詞，朱凱廸已有多宗案件纏身，朱太對出入法庭早不陌生，反應相對平靜，更不時以筆紀錄案情，希望有助丈夫解困。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/iWp9OcPQ2otnYYr0sgkQe9lQVf0=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7JUFQVYQFFGH5KOHUU5LRHE44U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FiWp9OcPQ2otnYYr0sgkQe9lQVf0%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7JUFQVYQFFGH5KOHUU5LRHE44U.jpg&h=a626220b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n施德來的太太"}]}